compromise legislation that would further restrict lobbying by 
former executive branch officials and apply lobbying restraints to 
former members of congress for the first time the legislation 
would bar departing members of congress from lobbying their former 
colleagues in either chamber for one year 
a 15 billion authorization for corps of engineers flood 
control and navigation projects in 12 states 
three houseapproved bills aimed at focusing the governments 
longrange aviation research boosting the commercial satellite 
industry and bringing order to federal superconductivity efforts 
